Package: SpaDES.docs
Title: Helper Utilities For Creating SpaDES Module Documentation And Manuals
Description: This package groups several functions used to create SpaDES module manuals in Rmarkdown format output to HTML and LaTeX.
URL: https://github.com/PredictiveEcology/SpaDES.docs
